ure modes. A distinct code (e.g., TRANSIENT_RETRY_EXHAUSTED) would be cleaner.","line":81}]},"followUpAttempts":0},"startedAt":"2026-06-10T11:54:56.138Z","endedAt":"2026-06-10T11:58:30.167Z"}
